title: Johara Complete Care Toothpaste 100gm
description:
Product details of Johara Complete Care Toothpaste 100g

  • Ayurveda Inspired. Clinically Validated.
  • Free from Paraben, Sulphate, Formaldehyde, Synthetic Dye.
  • Fluoride free formulation – Fluoride is considered as poison by FDA.
  • No animal ingredients. No Animal testing. 100%Vegetarian.
  • Supports in providing Clean, White & Strong Teeth.
  • Regular usage of Complete Care Toothpaste will fight the incidence of caries and plaque.
  • Sodium Lauryl Sulfate (SLS) free. SLS can cause or irritate existing allergies, canker sores and bad breath.
  • Formulated with Standardized Tetrahydrocurcumin from turmeric extracts, known as a powerful potent anti-oxidant and anti-inflammatory.
  • Enriched with MonoAmmonium Glycyrrhizinate (MAG) from Licorice known to inhibit the formation of dental caries.
  • Has a powerful anti-bacterial natural ingredient – Limonoids which is standardized to 50% sourced from the seeds of the neem tree.
  • RDA testing was done in Indiana University - School of Dentistry, Oral Health Research Institute, USA.
  • RDA score of less than 67, considered very low abrasion and hence gentle on the enamel of tooth.
  • Natural ingredients like spearmint, clove oil, anise oil, ginger, thymol and vanilla give you a refreshing cool breath.
  • Halal certified.
  • Complete Care – Provides fresh breath, healthy gum, clean, strong white teeth, fights incidence of cavities and soothe and counteracts periodontal diseases.
